{
  "stem": "10825.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- and then I perpetuated my musical studies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When I grew older, I learned even a trade.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My-- one brother of mine was a photographer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he had a studio.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I learned a trade in order to go to Warsaw and to perpetuate my studies and to be able to work, to support myself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I did, but I went too late.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was in-- in 19-- I went in the end of 1937.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I was there 1938.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was already before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And-- and it was very unpleasant for Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents' names were, my father was Mosze Spitzman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother was Rysia Tokman, maiden name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was a designer of ladies shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I grew up, he was-- he had only a store and sold shoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had one worker who was sitting and making shoes for ladies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a specialty that my father designed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like custom, before they started to bring in from factories, shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he was a specialist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he was a very social person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He belonged to the shul.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was on the board of the shul.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was president of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was a special organization to help poor people medically.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a doctor and a nurse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and the [? youths ?] then, who belonged to [INAUDIBLE], played theater.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The money that they made went for the-- for the organization.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had groups that-- in Europe, it was very popular to go into the street and to-- and to sell, like a flower or a pin.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, like, from paper flowers, made the pin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And with-- with [NON-ENGLISH], with-- with the-- the-- and the money went to it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
